news.title: US regulator sues Berkshire owned lender for making risky home loans
news.para: Vanderbilt Mortgage and Finance, a unit of Clayton, allegedly ignored "clear and obvious red flags" that borrowers could not afford their loans, and failed to properly assess borrowers' ability to pay other debts and keep food on the table.

news.title: Madhya Pradesh: MPIDC acquires 400 hectare of land to develop Vikram Udyogpuri phase II
news.para: At present, Vikram Udyogpuri spans 458 hectare and is nearly at full capacity. The process of taking possession of the new land has already began, and a detailed project report will be prepared to initiate the development.

news.title: Tamil Nadu: Construction work of Trichy Tidel park to begin this month
news.para: City corporation sources said 14.1 acre of land on Trichy-Madurai NH, adjacent to the upcoming integrated bus terminus (IBT), has been allocated to Tidel management for building the park in two phases.
